sect2.para:
XPixmapFormatValues
The
XPixmapFormatValues
structure provides an interface to the pixmap format information
that is returned at the time of a connection setup.
It contains:

typedef struct {
	int depth;
	int bits_per_pixel;
	int scanline_pad;
} XPixmapFormatValues;

listitem.para:
It disowns all selections owned by the client
(see 
).
